        <div class="pagination">
                                                                                                              <div id="showprevious" style="display:none;"><h3>David Jackson, New Editor of the <em class="emphitalic">American Journal of Physics</em></h3><p></p></div>
          
                    <a class="link_shownextprevious" alt="showprevious" href="http://ajp.aapt.org.libproxy1.nus.edu.sg/resource/1/ajpias/v79/i9/p893_s1?view=fulltext">Previous</a> Article
                
                |
                
                                                        <div id="shownext" style="display:none;"><h3>Measuring radon concentration in air using a diffusion cloud chamber</h3><p>
Radon concentration in air is a major concern in lung cancer studies. A traditional technique used to measure radon abundance is the charcoal canister method. We propose a novel technique using a diffusion cloud chamber. This technique is simpler and can easily be used for physics demonstrations for high school and university students.
</p></div>
                    <a class="link_shownextprevious" alt="shownext" href="http://ajp.aapt.org.libproxy1.nus.edu.sg/resource/1/ajpias/v79/i9/p903_s1?view=fulltext">Next</a> Article
          
            </div>

      
              		</div>
                                <div class="fulltext-headmeta">
                                        
                                          
                    
	                 
							<div class="abstitle">
		        <h1>
		        Using plasma experiments to illustrate a complex index of refraction
		        		        </h1>
		        		        		        
		        		    </div>
				
		                 
                
            
      
      
                        
        
        
        
                                                                                                                  
                                
        
            <span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1119/1.3591341&amp;rft.issn=19432909&amp;rft.title=American Journal of Physics&amp;rft.atitle=Using plasma experiments to illustrate a complex index of refraction&amp;rft.stitle=Am. J. Phys.&amp;rft.volume=79&amp;rft.issue=9&amp;rft.spage=894&amp;rft.epage=902&amp;rft.coden=AJPIAS"></span>

            
          
	                 
                                               
                    <script type="text/javascript">
               $(document).ready(function(){ 
                    
                });
           </script>
                            
            <div class="fulltext_authors_block">
                   
        
